  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crooked businessman KANE has taken over the city. Can the <strong>EIGHT DRAGONS</strong> take it back?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eight Dragons</strong> is a thrilling <strong>beat 'em up</strong> that delivers classic <strong>arcade</strong> action for up to eight players! Battle through a crime-ridden city in this action-packed <strong>side scroller</strong>, where fists, feet, and improvised weapons crush waves of relentless <strong>enemies</strong>. Take control of one of eight unique <strong>characters</strong>, each with their own story, fighting style, and path to defeat the sinister Kane and his criminal empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/1971b91ffa80d7b1695727c434d05756.poster.avif?t=1749139600\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/1971b91ffa80d7b1695727c434d05756.webm?t=1749139600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/cb511d33a0c254192ef84b8780fca700.webp?t=1749139600\" width=185 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic Co-op Gameplay</strong>: Team up with up to <strong>8 players</strong> in local or online <strong>multiplayer</strong>, blending individual stories for a dynamic <strong>brawler</strong> experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/8a6f836749ad866f8f7cec9778e30d54.poster.avif?t=1749139600\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/8a6f836749ad866f8f7cec9778e30d54.webm?t=1749139600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/8ec442750157362a84b6aab8a0c6420d.webp?t=1749139600\" width=320 height=44 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Arcade Action</strong>: Dive into fast-paced <strong>fighting</strong> with adjustable difficulty and speed, perfect for casual or hardcore fans.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Character Paths</strong>: Each Dragon’s journey intertwines, unlocking a deeper narrative and epic showdowns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Side-Scrolling Combat</strong>: Smash through <strong>enemies</strong> in vibrant <strong>2D</strong> pixel art, with intuitive controls for any controller or keyboard.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/65c44c6680ec087e7074a00ca0daff1b.poster.avif?t=1749139600\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/65c44c6680ec087e7074a00ca0daff1b.webm?t=1749139600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716250/extras/a0340f33fec88f35a375100d1f20e639.webp?t=1749139600\" width=212 height=49 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>adjustable game speed and difficulty</strong>, you can make the game as hard, easy, fast or slow as you like!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive the golden age of <strong>arcade brawlers</strong> and reclaim the city with <strong>Eight Dragons</strong>!</p>",
